data.description: Cute and quaint ranch style home with 4BR on the main floor! Beautiful hardwood flooring in living room and carried out into dining room/hallway. Kitchen is open to dining room and has great counter space, all appliances included, and newly done tile flooring. Furnace and a/c both installed new in 2018! Fresh coat of paint on the exterior of the home plus a new fence recently installed! Basement is unfinished and includes utility area and washer/dryer area -- the washer/dryer are included in sale of home! 1 stall attached garage, and property sits on a corner lot!
